Generic parsing framework for Twitter, Instagram, and Facebook.  
Please ignore for this project

Load JSON dataset from 
Social Search website 
based on a search term.
Filter images and only use JPG because the ML model is only expecting these image types

Call the ML Model through the API 
running on the edge node.
Extract the ML model response and convert to JSON

Convert results to CSV, 
merge rows, 
and write into CSV record to CDP
